title: Week 4 NFL Recap, Analysis; Redskins force Haskins into action (Football 9/30)
description:
Will Brinson is joined by Ryan Wilson, John Breech and Sean Wagner-McGough to recap all the Week 4 Sunday action from around the NFL. The guys discuss all 13 games on the Sunday slate including Cowboys-Saints (3:45), Panthers-Texans (12:00), Redskins-Giants (22:45), Patriots-Bills (33:45), Bucs-Rams (49:30), Vikings-Bears (1:00:15), Browns-Ravens (1:07:30), Chiefs-Lions (1:12:45), Jags-Broncos (1:19:00), Titans-Falcons, Raiders-Colts, Chargers-Dolphins (1:31:30) and Seahawks-Cardinals (1:38:00).
